1. *Mašina* je pokvarena. (The machine is broken.)
2. Molim vas, donesite mi *mašinu* za šivenje. (Please bring me the sewing machine.)
3. Želim da kupim novu *mašinu* za pranje veša. (I want to buy a new washing machine.)
4. *Mašina* za kafu radi sjajno. (The coffee machine works great.)
5. Popravio sam *mašinu* za sudove. (I fixed the dishwasher.)
6. *Mašinu* za mlevenje mesa treba pažljivo koristiti. (The meat grinder should be used carefully.)
7. *Mašinu* za sečenje drveta koristimo samo za velike komade. (The wood cutting machine is only used for large pieces.)
8. Završio sam sa korišćenjem *mašine* za vežbanje. (I finished using the exercise machine.)
9. U fabrici proizvode *mašine* za proizvodnju automobila. (The factory produces machines for car manufacturing.)
10. Radnici su popravili *mašinu* u fabrici. (The workers fixed the machine in the factory.)

Note: The Serbian word "mašinu" is in the accusative case in all of these sentences, as it is the direct object of the verb.